Steering deploy sequence: review the diff and scratch retro → commit/push → rebuild the CLI binary → restart the host worker from the monorepo checkout → `PUT http://127.0.0.1:3111/api/inngest` → verify `memory-retro-writer` registration → run `joelclaw retro <closed-brief>` and inspect the run/OTel/write receipt.
